Huntington_Park.Jonathan Club:
Jonathan Club is a private social club at two California locations—one in Downtown Los Angeles on South Figueroa Street and the other on the beach in Santa Monica. The club was included on the Platinum Club list of John Sibbald Associates in 2012 as one of the top five city clubs in the United States.


== History ==
The club was at one time believed to be named after Jonathan Trumbull, advisor to George Washington.
